{"tid":1538892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"撤回又點？9月8號一樣出來！！！！！","createTime":"2019-09-04T08:10:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T08:27:50.000Z","uid":162866,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"05f24e584b739b983d2bb8d486f5db8655f0dccd","tid":1538892,"uid":162866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:10:10.000Z","msg":"我地依家上街既目的唔再係為一條條例<br />\n<br />\n而係為自由正義同死去既手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n9月8約定你"},{"pid":"17cde4b32c1963d6fdc80b1685bdce1ead15aab7","tid":1538892,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:10:23.000Z","msg":"大家要到幾時先察覺，靠政府去實現五大訴求已經變成一個好恐怖既局？<br />\n<br />\n[時光倒流Re-post] 香港民權抗爭&mdash;&mdash;五大訴求，缺一不可？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538204</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先大家可以選擇服用咗以上文章先<br />\n<br />\n然後我可以反問一句，有冇人諗過五大訴求真係實現既情況會係點？<br />\n<br />\n係，的確可能證實到瘋狂既民意係可以改變到政府所作出既決定，但下次兩地一檢呢？再下次智慧燈柱、全面普教中呢？反送中2.0、3.0發生，真係好？點解要跟住個垃圾政權條尾走？<br />\n<br />\n香港人，唔好再「<span style=\"color: red;\">要求</span>」政府畀到五個願望你哋，請大家一齊親手達成依五個，甚至一百個願望都得，可唔可以？<br />\n<br />\n睇唔明我講咩既話請讀上面篇文章一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6ea64b33733aba230cc6a51c69778e3140ef494","tid":1538892,"uid":162866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:12:12.000Z","msg":"9月8"},{"pid":"a9144444a11f762cb0bb46a27b9d35a8ae1345ab","tid":1538892,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:12:45.000Z","msg":"政府愛國班子要共享大灣區繁榮"},{"pid":"0baa2b11737530c01457ca051a0ee4587e80b688","tid":1538892,"uid":162866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:14:52.000Z","msg":"9月8"},{"pid":"97f57df5885e16416b679f76b56d793e6606045c","tid":1538892,"uid":52407,"like":0,"dislike":