By":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:16:15.000Z","msg":"Let's promise each other<br />\nwe won't give up until all five demands are met"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:22:57.000Z","msg":"Promise has been made<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b3b03abb2a3ecaef3d4a23463f23bb619f15338","tid":1538892,"uid":72800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:24:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xcgb58P.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxcgb58P.gif&h=4c045c7d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ep8qq8P.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEp8qq8P.gif&h=b74f62eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong><em><div style=\"text-align: center;\">毋忘七烈 千一義 四眼 三十骨折 手腳筋<br />\n721元朗 811警暴 831車廂 雙肺 一裙<br />\n無數屈辱私刑 重傷昏迷<br />\n<br />\n撤回 定性 釋士 究警 普選</div></em></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港共殺人政權企圖以<strong>錄音、撤回、學季開始</strong><br />\n轉移<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">太子地鐵傷亡、<br />\n六警壓脊椎休克 至今嚴重昏迷、<br />\n新屋嶺、民主人權法案、<br />\n臥底實彈</span></strong></span>連串<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>核彈</strong></span><span style=\"color: red;\">事件焦點<br />\n醒呀大家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政府帶緊風向</span><br />\n背後繼續大清算 入獄 利刑 一年後被失蹤</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">暗黑兵法劇本 出沒注意：\n\n沒收gear 未來兩星期大量武警喬裝示威者 嫁禍衝擊\n內部分化示威者、\n酷刑凌虐威嚇被捕人士、\n邊緣打壓香港 渲染港獨 阻抗爭之風蔓延內陸、\n假新聞、擺拍、編輯、洗腦文宣製造風向 污名化運動、\n暴力鎮壓 拘捕 扣留 私刑 企圖瓦解前線、\n文宣 抹黑 嫁禍 插贜 示威者、\n暗殺 第一滴血 企圖逆轉民意 國際譴責、\n市民絕望噤聲 憤怒冷卻、\n中立派 賺錢派 政治疲勞、\n鼓吹經濟下滑風向 富豪商家屈服 加速瓦解、\n學季始開，拖延 分散 擊破、\n白色恐怖、清除異己、染紅香港\n\n拖字訣 雨傘結局 ⋯</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n袋住先 放風降溫<br />\n大追捕 清算 正式開始<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>這不只是反修例活動<br />\n這是屬於香港人的<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時代革命</span></strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"aaebb3e22b67c15cef0c983ae62bc495aba0e4e0","tid":1538892,"uid":196604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05f24e584b739b983d2bb8d486f5db8655f0dccd","tid":1538892,"uid":162866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:10:10.000Z","msg":"我地依家上街既目的唔再係為一條條例<br />\n<br />\n而係為自由正義同死去既手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n9月8約定你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:24:40.000Z","msg":"唔好意思阻一阻你個位。<br />\n<br />\n我地大家唔好辜負所有付出過，或者已經離開左既義士。 我地係唔會忘記佢地。<br />\n<br />\n我地要贏，贏係要贏晒！唔係輸4球比人！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1537433\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1537433</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fIpRoDyLaws\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FfIpRoDyLaws&d=s4T%2BQ7CxF5mM3MMXIC%2FEq0VeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=048a4025\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fIpRoDyLaws</a>"},{"pid":"2416447f76c2abcc5b97733e6656ab7cdee0f70e","tid":1538892,"uid":241904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:27:50.000Z","msg":"佢而家撤回根本係想我地8/9少人出黎,咁9/9美國復會就未必過到香港人權關係法<br />\n撤回係3個月前既訴求<br />\n而家係五大訴求,缺一不可<br />\n如果唔係只會每幾年就有一過revolution"}]}